lead_paragraph: Still searching for consistency after suffering a back injury, Park In-bee is delighted to be in familiar surroundings as she embarks on her defense of the HSBC Women's Champions in Singapore this week.

headline.print_headline: Park Seeks Repeat Win on Return to Happy Hunting Ground
